Class ContentTransferAgentS3.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.philcali.device.pool.s3.ContentTransferAgentS3.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    ContentTransferAgentS3
    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class ContentTransferAgentS3.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type ContentTransferAgentS3. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
